{"text_id":117814,"tokens":["During"," the"," ","1","9","th"," century",","," when"," the"," British"," Empire"," was"," expanding"," into"," southern"," Africa",","," the"," indigenous"," tribes",","," such"," as"," the"," Zulu"," and"," X","hosa",","," had"," varying"," levels"," of"," awareness"," regarding"," the"," size"," and"," scope"," of"," the"," British"," Empire","."," It"," is"," important"," to"," note"," that"," their"," understanding"," was"," largely"," influenced"," by"," their"," direct"," interactions"," with"," the"," British"," and"," other"," European"," powers",","," rather"," than"," a"," comprehensive"," grasp"," of"," the"," global"," reach"," of"," the"," Empire",".","\n\n","The"," Zulu"," kingdom",","," under"," the"," leadership"," of"," Sha","ka",","," had"," experienced"," conflicts"," with"," European"," traders"," and"," settlers"," before"," the"," formal"," colonization"," by"," the"," British","."," However",","," their"," primary"," concern"," was"," the"," protection"," of"," their"," territory"," and"," people"," from"," these"," intrusions",","," rather"," than"," an"," understanding"," of"," the"," broader"," political"," context"," of"," the"," British"," Empire","."," It"," was"," only"," after"," the"," Anglo","-","Zulu"," War"," in"," ","1","8","7","9"," that"," the"," Zulu"," would"," have"," gained"," a"," clearer"," picture"," of"," the"," military"," might"," and"," territorial"," ambitions"," of"," the"," British",".","\n\n","The"," X","hosa",","," on"," the"," other"," hand",","," had"," longer"," and"," more"," intense"," interactions"," with"," the"," British",","," culminating"," in"," a"," series"," of"," frontier"," wars","."," The"," X","hosa"," would"," have"," been"," more"," exposed"," to"," the"," breadth"," of"," British"," influence",","," but"," their"," awareness"," was"," still"," limited"," to"," their"," immediate"," region","."," The"," X","hosa",","," like"," many"," other"," African"," tribes","